item.title: A second Post
item.description: A lot more Wise words. You think water moves fast? You should see ice. It moves like it has a mind. Like it knows it killed the world once and got a taste for murder. After the avalanche, it took us a week to climb out. Now, I don’t know exactly when we turned on each other, but I know that seven of us survived the slide… and only five made it out.

item.title: First Post
item.description: Yeah, but your scientists were so preoccupied with whether or not they could, they didn’t stop to think if they should. Jaguar shark! So tell me - does it really exist? Remind me to thank John for a lovely weekend. Hey, you know how I’m, like, always trying to save the planet? Here’s my chance. Must go faster… go, go, go, go, go! You really think you can fly that thing?
